long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a free extension for dutching calculation between 2 and up to 8 selections.
This is a free dutching calculator provided by White Label Sportsbook SRL (www.white-label-sportsbook.net). 

The extension allows the user to calculate required wagers and outcome for up to 8 selections on a single sports market.

White Label Sportsbook SRL is the a premium provider of white label sportsbook software, data feeds, high-performance hosting for sports betting websites, online casinos and poker websites.

Our white label sportsbook pricing model is based on a plain simple yearly subscription. Our fees cover everything required to operate, from software, graphic design and branding, market data and up to customer support. There are no other hidden fees or costs.

This application/extension does not collect any data from its users in any way, shape or form.
